metadata.name: Forest guardian
metadata.description:
The Dryad is a beautiful and magical creature shrouded in mystery. She is kind and gentle, devoting her life to the protection of nature and its creatures.

This fragile-looking girl possesses great power, she has dominion over the earth, its creatures and plants. She can summon powerful winds to change the shape of the earth, animals, and plants to bend to her will, and summon rain or lightning at her will.
